      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph props="autonumber">1552.216-73</ph> Fixed rates for services - indefinite delivery/indefinite quantity contract.</title>
      <conbody>
         <p xtrc="P">As prescribed in <xref outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref "
                  base="Section_1516_505_T48_601314311"
                  href="Section_1516_505_T48_601314311.dita#Section_1516_505_T48_601314311">1516.505</xref>(b), insert the following clause to specify fixed rates for services in indefinite delivery/indefinite quantity contracts. When the contract contains options, the clause should be modified to reflect the information and data for the base period and any option periods. 
</p>
                                    <p xtrc="HD1">Fixed Rates for Services - Indefinite Delivery/Indefinite Quantity Contract (APR 1984)
</p>
                                    <p xtrc="P">The following fixed rates shall apply for payment purposes for the duration of the contact. 
</p>
